        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <p class="lead">What is <a href="http://ogp.me">Open Graph?</a></p>
          <p class="blurb">
            Open Graph is a metadata protocol enables any web page to become a rich object. 
            This is used by Facebook and other services to embed content in a native and easy 
            to understand manner.
          </p>
          <p class="blurb">Open Graph uses standard HTTP meta tags to mark up content for easy consumption.</p>
